data_table.description: Form 31 - Reproductive History -- age at menarche; history of menstrual irregularity and amenorrhea; history of menopausal symptoms; history of pregnancy, pregnancy outcomes, infertility; history of breast feeding; history of gynecologic and breast surgeries.
